description.en:
Our Generation Rock N' Sweet Hair doll accessories

Add a touch of rock and glamour to your life with the Rock n Sweet Hair doll accessories! These hair accessories include beautiful clips and pins, from which you can turn any doll into a rock star. This set for 18-inch dolls is full of flash and flair for hair!

Specifications:
Color: multicolor
Gender: girls
Material: plastic, felt
Dimensions packaging: 31,8 x 22,8 x 5 cm (L x W x D)
Suitable for dolls: 18 inch (45 cm)
Age: 3 years and up

Contents:
1 Glitter headband
2 Pom-pom felt headbands
1 Hair comb with bows
3 Bow clips
2 Ombre hair extensions
4 Hair elastics
8 Hairpins
1 Hair elastic pearl beads
2 Hairclips hearts
2 Hairpins stars
